VERSION 3 IS NOW RELEASED - COME TRY OUT IMPROVED FPS, BETTER GRAPHICS, SEXY HDR LIGHTING AND MUCH MORE!

This is a fun map based around the command sv_friction 0. You use left and right strafe to gain speed and slide around the map, once you have gained enough speed you can try thejramps and attempt to get to the leap of faith to get a better weapon!

Just try it, you will be addicted from the word "Let's move out"
